title: GENI plots
text: geni.plots R package tool visualising results genome-wide association studies (GWAS) phenome-wide association studies (PheWAS). package can currently produce Manhattan plots, quantile-quantile (QQ) plots, regional plots using GWAS summary statistics using fig_manhattan(), fig_qq(), fig_region() functions, respectively. addition, PheWAS plots can constructed using fig_phewas() function.
code: library(dplyr) library(geni.plots)

title: GENI plots
text: package contains following functions: fig_manhattan: creates Manhattan plot genomic markers across genome, e.g. results genome-wide association studies. fig_phewas: creates plot visualising results phenome-wide association studies (PheWAS). fig_qq: creates quantile-quantile (QQ) plot. fig_region: creates regional plot, .e. scatter graph genomic markers associations (e.g. log10(p-values)) gene bar underneath. fig_stack_region: creates stacked regional association plot.

title: GENI plots
text: package contains formatted test data downloaded FinnGen r9 (1:154426970--C) GWAS studies IL6 (GCST90274815) IL6R (GCST90274815) levels GWAS Catalog server. geni_test_manhattan- data.frame results GWAS interleukin-6 levels p-values < 1e-3 (GCST90274815). genomic coordinates used GRCh37. description data can viewed using help(geni_test_gwas). geni_test_phewas- data.frame PheWAS results rs FinnGen r9 (1:154426970--C). description data can viewed using help(geni_test_phewas). assoc - data.frame results GWAS interleukin-6 levels GRCh37 region 1:154301970-154551970 (GCST90274815). genomic coordinates used GRCh37. description data can viewed using help(geni_test_region). corr - matrix correlation statistics markers assoc using European samples 1000 Genomes Phase 3. genomic coordinates used GRCh37. assoc - data.frame results GWAS studies interleukin-6 interleukin 6 receptor levels GRCh37 region 1:154301970-154551970 (GCST90274815 GCST90088597). genomic coordinates used GRCh37. description data can viewed using help(geni_test_region). corr - matrix correlation statistics markers assoc using European samples 1000 Genomes Phase 3. genomic coordinates used GRCh37.
